elter Plan 2017-2025\" />{{rp|34}}\n|-\n|Barangay 87 || 8 || Calaanan East (EDSA)\n|-\n|Barangay 88 || 8 || Calaanan East (Rizal Avenue Extension)\n|-\n|Barangay 89 || 8 || Calaanan East (11th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 90 || 8 || Our Lady of Grace (11th Avenue)<ref name=\"Caloocan City Local Shelter Plan 2017-2025\" />{{rp|34}}\n|-\n|Barangay 91 || 8 || Our Lady of Grace (11th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 92 || 8 || Barrio Rodriguez (11th Avenue)<ref name=\"Caloocan City Local Shelter Plan 2017-2025\" />{{rp|34}}\n|-\n|Barangay 93 || 8 || Barrio Rodriguez (11th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 94 || 9 || Calaanan East (EDSA)\n|-\n|Barangay 95 || 9 || Balintawak\n|-\n|Barangay 96 || 9 || Calaanan East (EDSA)\n|-\n|Barangay 97 || 9 || Barrio Galino (11th Avenue)<ref name=\"Caloocan City Local Shelter Plan 2017-2025\" />{{rp|34}}\n|-\n|Barangay 98 || 9 || Balintawak\n|-\n|Barangay 99 || 9 || Balintawak (Dorotea Compund)\n|-\n|Barangay 100 || 9 || Balintawak\n|-\n|Barangay 101 || 9 || Barrio Galino (10th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 102 || 9 || Barrio Galino (10th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 103 || 9 || Our Lady of Grace (10th Avenue)<ref name=\"Caloocan City Local Shelter Plan 2017-2025\" />{{rp|35}}\n|-\n|Barangay 104 || 9 || Our Lady of Grace (10th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 105 || 9 || Barrio Galino (8th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 106 || 10 || Our Lady of Grace (10th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 107 || 10 || Our Lady of Grace (10th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 108 || 10 || Our Lady of Grace (10th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 109 || 10 || Our Lady of Grace (8th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 110 || 10 || Grace Park East (7th Avenue)<ref name=\"Caloocan City Comprehensive Land Use Plan 2019\" />{{rp|244}}\n|-\n|Barangay 111 || 10 || Grace Park East (7th Avenue)\n|- \n|Barangay 112 || 10 || Grace Park East (7th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 113 || 10 || Grace Park East (6th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 114 || 10 || Grace Park East (6th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 115 || 10 || Grace Park East (6th Avenue)\n|-\n|Barangay 116 || 10 || Grace Park East (